76
00:08:42,820 --> 00:08:45,830
He's way outside the limits of army regs.

77
00:08:45,910 --> 00:08:48,330
They wanna fly with you for some reason.

78
00:08:48,410 --> 00:08:50,330
I guess it's 'cause they think you're the best.

79
00:08:50,410 --> 00:08:52,960
It's 'cause I only recruit the dumb ones, sir.

80
00:08:57,130 --> 00:08:59,090
I don't suppose I have a choice in all this.

81
00:08:59,130 --> 00:09:01,840
You sure don't.

82
00:09:02,930 --> 00:09:04,590
Wouldn't miss it for the world.

83
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:07,140
To the Air Cav.

84
00:09:15,110 --> 00:09:16,520
Good mornin', Sergeant Major.

85
00:09:16,610 --> 00:09:19,570
How do you know what kind of goddamn day it is?

86
00:09:27,330 --> 00:09:30,750
Group! Atten-hut!

87
00:09:55,100 --> 00:09:57,190
At ease, gentlemen.

88
00:09:58,940 --> 00:10:01,030
Welcome to the new cavalry.

89
00:10:02,530 --> 00:10:04,490
We will ride into battle.

90
00:10:05,780 --> 00:10:08,780
And this... will be our horse.

91
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:37,100
You don't have to catch it. You don't have to feed it.

92
00:10:38,730 --> 00:10:40,230
But I can assure you...

93
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:45,610
